{"route":{"route":"/posts/4b39445f/","outputPath":"posts/4b39445f/index.html","kind":"post","title":"DNS over HTTPS","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"4b39445f"}},"description":"这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章 DNS EDNS DNSSEC DNS over HTTPS 完整代码请看DNS DOH就比较简单了,因为DOH使用的请求数据和应答数据均为之前的DNS协议格式,包括DNS,EDNS,DNSSEC...当然是否支持EDNS,DNSSEC需要看DNS服务器的支持情况 DOH的最主要的区别","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/DNS-over-HTTPS.md","route":"/posts/4b39445f/","abbrlink":"4b39445f","title":"DNS over HTTPS","date":"2020-06-23 00:30:08","updated":"2020-06-23 00:30:08","tags":["DNS","DOH","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章<br>\n<a href=\"/posts/f05986bf/\">DNS</a>  <a href=\"/posts/668530ca/\">EDNS</a> <a href=\"/posts/1751943e/\">DNSSEC</a> <a href=\"/posts/4b39445f/\">DNS over HTTPS</a> 完整代码请看<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/tree/master/net/dns\">DNS</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>DOH就比较简单了,因为DOH使用的请求数据和应答数据均为之前的DNS协议格式,包括DNS,EDNS,DNSSEC…当然是否支持EDNS,DNSSEC需要看DNS服务器的支持情况<br>\nDOH的最主要的区别是把DNS使用的UDP,换成了HTTPS,这样就能防止DNS污染了,而且可以使用DNSSEC加上ESNI来防止证书劫持,DOH的协议在<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8484\">rfc8484</a>中有定义<br>\nDOH主要有两种方式HTTP的GET请求和POST的请求</p>\n<h2 id=\"get\">GET</h2>\n<p>GET请求需要使用BASE64对请求的字节数据进行序列化,然后作为参数传递,获取到的数据使用我们之前的解析进行解析就行了</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">get</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(dReq []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, server <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>)</span></span> (body []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, err <span class=\"hljs-type\">error</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> query := strings.Replace(base64.URLEncoding.EncodeToString(dReq), <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> urls := <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;https://&quot;</span> + server + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/dns-query?dns=&quot;</span> + query</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> res, err := http.Get(urls)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">defer</span> res.Body.Close()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> body, err = ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"post\">POST</h2>\n<p>POST并不需要进行序列化,直接把原始请求数据作为body就行了</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">post</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(dReq []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, server <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>)</span></span> (body []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, err <span class=\"hljs-type\">error</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> client := &amp;http.Client{Timeout: <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span> * time.Second}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req, err := http.NewRequest(http.MethodPost, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, bytes.NewReader(dReq))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, fmt.Errorf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;DOH:post() newReq -&gt; %v&quot;</span>, err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> urls, err := url.Parse(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;//&quot;</span> + server)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, fmt.Errorf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;DOH:post() urlParse -&gt; %v&quot;</span>, err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.URL.Scheme = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;https&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.URL.Host = urls.Host</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.URL.Path = urls.Path + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/dns-query&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.Header.Set(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;accept&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;application/dns-message&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.Header.Set(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;application/dns-message&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> req.ContentLength = <span class=\"hljs-type\">int64</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(dReq))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> resp, err := client.Do(req)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, fmt.Errorf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;DOH:post() req -&gt; %v&quot;</span>, err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">defer</span> resp.Body.Close()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> body, err = ioutil.ReadAll(resp.Body)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, fmt.Errorf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;DOH:post() readBody -&gt; %v&quot;</span>, err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>完整代码请看开头</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8484\">rfc8484</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"get","text":"GET","level":2},{"id":"post","text":"POST","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"4b39445f","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}